    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "what do you mean by reevaluate? i feel like i've already tried everything. i go to work, i eat, i sleep... but it's all just going through the motions. it's like i'm already a ghost, just waiting for my body to catch up to how dead i feel inside. what's even the point of \"moving forward\" when the person i was moving towards is gone?",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
